FBIS4-34527 "drlat119_p_94004" FBIS-LAT-94-119 Daily Report 21 Jun 1994 Ecuador Daily Announces Series of Opinion Polls Daily Announces Series of Opinion Polls 94P20878 94P20878 CSO [Editorial Report] Guayaquil EL UNIVERSO 0F 30 May announces that the results of a series of opinion polls conducted by Informe Confidencial will be published on page 1 of the newspaper, four times a week: Monday, Tuesday, Saturday, and Sunday. The polls will be conducted among residents of Guayaquil and Quito in an attempt to gather public opinion on various issues of national concern. ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |First Poll: RETURN TO THE BALLOT BOX | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Question: Do You Think the Government Should Call a Plebiscite for July? | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Answer: |Yes |Guayaquil |57.3 percent|Quito |53 percent | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | |No |Guayaquil |36.5 percent|Quito |43.3 percent| ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | |No Answer |Guayaquil |6.2 percent |Quito |3.7 percent | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Source: Informe Confidencial | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
